title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Wrap the Karin Everon RS in the New Mosh Mosh Livery
content:
The Karin Everon RS (SUV) was already oversized and overpowered. Now add ‘over-the-top’ to that list by wrapping it in the brand new Mosh Mosh livery, available now from any Vehicle Workshop.

Plus, get your hands dirty this week with 2X GTA$ and LS Car Meet Rep for Auto Shop Client Jobs, 2X GTA$ for completing Document Forgery Sell Missions, and 3X GTA$ and RP on Madrazo Hits.
